{
  "stem": "13471.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And here I was, a mere lieutenant commander, you see.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, with them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On the same level, you see.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so-- and in the prosecution, I don't think-- the administration were all at least brigadier generals, you see.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] They had a few colonels, maybe.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But anyway--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, and also in the administrative side, outside the courtroom.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so-- and so the Navy had this routine called spot promotion.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If a-- If a-- one-- a Navy officer got into a certain position, and they felt that a temporary promotion to the next higher rank was in order, they would give him what they called a, quote, 'spot' promotion for that spot.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I got to thinking about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I thought, well, I ought to have a spot promotion.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I sent away, and I got the Navy's pamphlet detailing how you would be promoted on a spot promotion.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I looked through it, and I thought, well, I think I qualify.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I went down to see General Jill.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I call him Jill.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "His name was Gill, but you know, a jill is a half a pint, you see.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Well, that's about where we ranked the general--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was an Army brigadier general.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Our army.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he was my nearest superior, as far as we could figure out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So anyway, I went down to see General Jill.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I said General, I got the feeling that I ought to have-- ought to be qualified for a spot promotion.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And if you-- and I told him why.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And if you agree, now here's-- here's the Navy's regulations about how you do it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you write a letter, and you say this, and you say this, and you say this.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
